gg_snowzone
 A frosty and cold gun game map. Focuses around a large, abandoned, almost industrial-like building. Two hallways allow access around the map and a ramp down to the center of battle. Dedicateted to my friend MEAN_MARINE. (From your friends at atk) ;) -24 spawns- -soundscape- -func_precipitation- -hdr- -env_wind- Enjoy. by Tom_Tom92
